{"tid":2078557,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西總統被裁定必須戴罩","createTime":"2020-06-25T06:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T06:45:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00c4ea8a3153cd46f26e3170c2b582e57ab61ec7","tid":2078557,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200625/JXH4NQP2MAWFJDSI6U64EHVK2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200625%2FJXH4NQP2MAWFJDSI6U64EHVK2I%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfaNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=996c3ce0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200625%2FJXH4NQP2MAWFJDSI6U64EHVK2I%2F&h=8c782062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200625/JXH4NQP2MAWFJDSI6U64EHVK2I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n巴西總統被裁定必須戴罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YPryY1PwUTXuX5_wo1mhZUbtEEc=/190x106/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZCN4LLBRJAOMKB2XSHOZDGUQCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYPryY1PwUTXuX5_wo1mhZUbtEEc%3D%2F190x106%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZCN4LLBRJAOMKB2XSHOZDGUQCE.jpg&h=be67e955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n博爾索納羅<br />\n<br />\n巴西總統博爾索納羅自武漢肺炎爆發後多次違反抗疫措施，一名聯邦法官周一裁定他不可凌駕法律，下令他在首都巴西利亞活動時要戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法官︰沒人可凌駕憲法<br />\n<br />\n巴西利亞及周邊地區自4月底起強制民眾戴口罩，但博爾索納羅多次在公開露面期間不正確戴口罩甚至完全不戴口罩。法官博雷利（Renato Coelho Borelli）裁定，如果他繼續違例，須每日罰款2,000巴西雷亞爾（3,008港元）。<br />\n<br />\n博雷利說：「在<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n不尊重他人的行為，使他人健康承受風險。」<br />\n<br />\n他引述總統就職誓詞指會「捍衞和遵<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n是政府元首也不行。總統必須遵從所有抗疫措施」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》"},{"pid":"0c57843b159d1f9c3c2017e3d3b631adedfec961","tid":2078557,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"幾時到美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}